definition.text: The Superalgos repository features two main branches: master and develop.

translations.text: La repository di Superalgos ha tree branches principali: master, develop e quella che cerchiamo noi, plugins-docs.
L'entrepôt Superalgos comporte trois sections principales : master, develop, et celle que nous recherchons, plugins-docs.
El repositorio de Superalgos presenta tres ramas principales: master, develop, y el que estamos buscando, plugins-docs.
Das Superalgos-Repository hat zwei Hauptzweige: master und develop.
Репозиторий Superalgos имеет две основные ветви: master и develop.
Superalgos deposu iki ana dala sahiptir: Master ve Develop.

paragraphs.text: Master Branch: features the stable version of the software. Never submit contributions to this branch!

translations.text: Master Branch: ospita l'ultima versione stabile del software. Non mandare mai contributi a questo branch!
Branche Master: Features la version stable du logiciel. Ne soumettez jamais de contributions à cette branche !
Master Branch: Es la versión estable del software. ¡Nunca envíes contribuciones a esta rama!
Master Branch: Enthält die stabile Version der Software. Reichen Sie niemals Beiträge für diesen Zweig ein!
Master Branch: Представляет собой стабильную версию программного обеспечения. Никогда не вносите вклад в эту ветвь!
Master Branch: Yazılımın kararlı sürümünü içerir. Bu şubeye asla katkı göndermeyin!

paragraphs.text: Develop Branch: features the version currently in development. Submit contributions of code affecting the codebase, translations, improvements in the Docs, tutorials, and plugins such as data mines, trading systems, and so on!

translations.text: Develop Branch: contiene la versione attualmente in sviluppo. Manda qui i contributi riguardanti la codebase.
Branche Develop : Features la version en cours de développement., pour soumettre des contributions de code affectant la base de code.
Develop Branch: Presenta la versión actualmente en desarrollo. Envía contribuciones de código que afecten al código base.

Develop Branch: Enthält die Version, die sich derzeit in der Entwicklung befindet. Reichen Sie Beiträge ein, die die Codebasis, Übersetzungen,Verbesserungen der Docs, Tutorials, plugins sowie Data-Mines, trading systems und so weiter betreffen.

Develop Branch: Представляет версию, находящуюся в разработке. Вносите свой вклад в код, затрагивающий кодовую базу, переводы, улучшения в документации, учебники и плагины, такие как источники данных, торговые системы и так далее!

Develop Branch: Şu anda geliştirilmekte olan sürümü içerir. Kod tabanını, çevirileri, Dokümanlardaki iyileştirmeleri, öğreticileri ve veri madenleri, ticaret sistemleri vb. gibi eklentileri etkileyen katkılarınızı bu dala gönderin!

paragraphs.text: Ignore the instructions to switch branches of the next few steps if you are not using the Contributors installation. Just click Next to continue.

translations.text: Contributors kurulumunu kullanmıyorsanız, sonraki birkaç adımdaki dal değiştirme talimatlarını dikkate almayın. Devam etmek için İleri'ye tıklayın.
